author: breser
msg: On svn-auth-x509 branch, Extend the win32_xlate code to support converting
from UTF-16 and UTF-32 Big Endian.
(get_page_id_from_name): Use new constants and clean up some formatting.
(svn_subr__win32_xlate_to_stringbuf): Add new code to handle the half of the
conversion from UTF-16/32 BE to UTF-8 that Windows can't do.  Also fix
formatting that didn't match our style while I'm at it.
